title: Multi-Model Debate / Consensus
---
For high-stakes tasks (code review, architectural decisions, factual research), route the same prompt to N models in parallel, then run a lightweight 'judge' prompt that compares responses, explains disagreements, and produces a synthesis with a confidence score. 'clawq agent --debate "Is this migration safe?"' uses 3 models and reports consensus. Dramatically reduces single-model hallucination risk. No other personal assistant offers built-in adversarial verification.